e><space><space><space><space><space><space><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>request_str<space>=<space>self.post_xml<openparen><closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>feature.setAttribute<openparen><apos>query_response<apos><comma><space>request_str<closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>self.pyoutput<openparen>feature<closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><lf><space><space><space><space>def<space>post_xml<openparen>self<closeparen>:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>headers<space>=<space><opencurly><apos>Content-Type<apos>:<space><apos>text<solidus>xml<semicolon><space>charset=utf-8<apos><closecurly><space>#<space>set<space>what<space>your<space>server<space>accepts<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>return<space>requests.post<openparen>self.csw_url<comma><space>data=self.xml_str<comma><space>headers=headers<comma><space>verify=False<closeparen>.text<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><lf><space><space><space><space>def<space>close<openparen>self<closeparen>:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>pass }    PY_OUTPUT_TAGS { PYOUTPUT <Rejected> }    OUTPUT { PYOUTPUT FEATURE_TYPE PyCSW_POST_4_OUTPUT         }    OUTPUT { <Rejected> FEATURE_TYPE PyCSW_POST_4_<Rejected>         }
